Package: rcpv
Type: Package
Title: Conversion of common procurement vocabulary (CPV) codes
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-12-18
Author: Michał Kaftanowicz
Maintainer: Michał Kaftanowicz <michal@kaftanowicz.com>
Description: The main function exported by this package is describe_cpv, which repairs given CPV codes if they are broken, classifies them at selected level of aggregation and returns their description in chosen language, shortened to desired number of characters.
License: MIT
LazyData: true
Imports: logging, data.table, stringi
